column2: If you had coffee today, at what time did you take your last cup of coffee?
column3: If you had alcohol today, at what time did you have your last drink?
column4: If you did a workout today, at what time did your last workout end?
column5: If you did a stress-relieving activity today (meditation, yoga, etc), at what time did you do your last one?
column6: Did you take medication that might affect your sleep?
column7: How much did you eat in the last 3 hours before going to bed?
column8: How would you characterize the activities you did in the last 3 hours before going to bed?
column9: How much stress and/or anxiety do you feel now?
column10: Is there any particular reason why you think you might or might not sleep well tonight?
